  - Title: Bhagavad-Gîtâ
    Location: II 69
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=Repentance, Renewal and Awakening
  - 934
  - 346
---
That which is night to all beings, therein the self-subjugated remains
awake; and in that where all beings are awake, that is night for the
knower of Self.
